7.10	Hiro_Protagonist	Snow Crash	Snow Crash is Neal Stephenson's third novel, published in 1992. Like many of Stephenson's other novels it covers history, linguistics, anthropology, archaeology, religion, computer science, politics, cryptography, memetics, and philosophy.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d5/Snowcrash.jpg/200px-Snowcrash.jpg
